data.description: Welcome home to this three bedroom, two and a half bath residence situated on a corner lot, providing additional privacy and a spacious feel. The interior features dark hardwood floors that extend throughout the entire house. The updated kitchen, boasts modern finishes and stainless steel appliances. With its open floor-plan, the kitchen seamlessly flows into the dining area and living space, creating a welcoming and functional layout. The open design allows for easy interaction and entertainment, making it an ideal space for gatherings. One notable feature of this property is the covered patio, providing a comfortable outdoor space to relax and enjoy the surroundings. The patio is perfect for outdoor dining, lounging, or simply enjoying a morning coffee while admiring the lush wooded views. Overall, this corner lot home offers a harmonious blend of style, functionality, and natural beauty. Start packing, your new home awaits! Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough.
